infos.urlText: Wynyard Station wheelchair access restrictions
infos.content:
The tunnel under George Street will be closed while construction work takes place. Please use the George Street exit to access Hunter Street and Pitt Street.

If you require wheelchair access to Wynyard Station please use the Carrington or York Street entrances and look for the highly visible concierge staff near the banners at the top and bottom of the George Street escalators who can provide assistance or alternative access if required. Concierge staff are in place from 6.30am to 8pm, 7 days a week.
infos.subtitle: Wynyard Station wheelchair access restrictions

infos.urlText: Weekend trackwork between Hurstville and Central. Trains run to a changed timetable
infos.content:
Friday 23, Saturday 24 and Sunday 25 November 
  • From 10.50pm Friday to 8am Saturday, and from 10pm Saturday to 9.20am Sunday, buses replace trains between Hurstville and Central.
  • Trains run to a changed timetable between Cronulla and Hurstville, between Waterfall and Sutherland or Hurstville and between Central and Bondi Junction.

On Saturday from 8am to 10pm, and Sunday from 9.20am to 10pm
  • Buses replace trains between Sydenham and Central
  • Trains run to a changed timetable between:
    - Cronulla and Sydenham
    - Waterfall and Sutherland or Hurstville
    - Central and Bondi Junction
  • If you are travelling to the City from Illawarra Line stations please change at Wolli Creek for a T8 Airport & South Line train to City Circle stations.
  • If you are travelling to stations between Central and Bondi Junction please change at Wolli Creek for a T8 Airport & South Line train to Central, then change for a train to Martin Place, Kings Cross, Edgecliff or Bondi Junction.
  • Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date information.

Bus routes
3AT4: Hurstville, then Central and return
5T4: Kogarah, Rockdale then Central and return
7T4: Hurstville, then all stations to Sydenham then Central and return (bypassing Tempe)
9T4: Tempe to Sydenham shuttle (minibus)
1T3: Sydenham, then all stations to Central and return
2T3: Sydenham, then Central and return
infos.subtitle: Weekend trackwork between Hurstville and Central. Trains run to a changed timetable

properties.speechText: From 10.50 PM Friday 23rd November to 10 PM Sunday 25th November, buses replace trains between Hurstville and Central. Buses also replace trains between Sydenham and Central. For more information go to transport n-s-w dot info.

infos.urlText: Wynyard Station wheelchair access restrictions
infos.content:
The tunnel under George Street will be closed while construction work takes place. Please use the George Street exit to access Hunter Street and Pitt Street.

If you require wheelchair access to Wynyard Station please use the Carrington or York Street entrances and look for the highly visible concierge staff near the banners at the top and bottom of the George Street escalators who can provide assistance or alternative access if required. Concierge staff are in place from 6.30am to 8pm, 7 days a week.

infos.urlText: Weekend trackwork between Hurstville and Central. Trains run to a changed timetable
infos.content:
Friday 23, Saturday 24 and Sunday 25 November 
  • From 10.50pm Friday to 8am Saturday, and from 10pm Saturday to 9.20am Sunday, buses replace trains between Hurstville and Central.
  • Trains run to a changed timetable between Cronulla and Hurstville, between Waterfall and Sutherland or Hurstville and between Central and Bondi Junction.

On Saturday from 8am to 10pm, and Sunday from 9.20am to 10pm
  • Buses replace trains between Sydenham and Central
  • Trains run to a changed timetable between:
    - Cronulla and Sydenham
    - Waterfall and Sutherland or Hurstville
    - Central and Bondi Junction
  • If you are travelling to the City from Illawarra Line stations please change at Wolli Creek for a T8 Airport & South Line train to City Circle stations.
  • If you are travelling to stations between Central and Bondi Junction please change at Wolli Creek for a T8 Airport & South Line train to Central, then change for a train to Martin Place, Kings Cross, Edgecliff or Bondi Junction.
  • Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date information.

Bus routes
3AT4: Hurstville, then Central and return
5T4: Kogarah, Rockdale then Central and return
7T4: Hurstville, then all stations to Sydenham then Central and return (bypassing Tempe)
9T4: Tempe to Sydenham shuttle (minibus)
1T3: Sydenham, then all stations to Central and return
2T3: Sydenham, then Central and return
infos.subtitle: Weekend trackwork between Hurstville and Central. Trains run to a changed timetable
